mory `JCEKS` keystores and a minimal test certificate.\\n- Converted two existing non-ASCII string literals to Unicode escapes without changing their runtime values, so Checkstyle passes.\\n\\nValidation:\\n- `./gradlew checkstyle -Pcoordinates=org.apache.kerby:kerby-util:1.0.1 --stacktrace` ✅\\n- `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.apache.kerby:kerby-util:1.0.1 --stacktrace` ✅\", \"textSignature\": \"{\\\"v\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"msg_0397fa87ee62bc940169f122580358819eaf1d420a9c1d441c\\\",\\\"phase\\\":\\\"final_answer\\\"}\"}], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 1877, \"output\": 454, \"cacheRead\": 57344, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 59675, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1777410644816, \"responseId\": \"resp_0397fa87ee62bc940169f122556774819ea0baac0e1ac7cac9\"}, \"toolResults\": []}\n","exit_code":0,"status":"completed"}}
